11/08/2009
SKOPJE, Macedonia -- Hundreds of Macedonians waited for hours Monday (August10th) to get new tickets to the national football team's upcoming match against Spain. 
The Macedonian Football Federation decided to replace tickets already sold amid reports that many unsuspecting fans had bought counterfeit tickets. 
Wednesday's big match in Skopje will mark 100 years of football in Macedonia. 
(Utrinski Vesnik, Dnevnik, Vecer - 11/08/09; A1, Makfax, Mina - 10/08/09)
